STATE of North Carolina
v.
Carl Lynn WILLIAMS No. 482P13-3 Supreme Court of North Carolina. May 28, 2019 N.C. Dept. of Justice, for State of North Carolina. Carl Lynn Williams, for Williams, Carl Lynn.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Petitioner on the 28th of May 2019 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Cumberland County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 28th of May 2019."
